Package: spark-store-tui
Version: 0.7.2-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: SilentByte <noreply@example.com>
Installed-Size: 26
Depends: bash (>= 4), curl, jq, fzf, aria2, ca-certificates
Recommends: chafa, sudo
Suggests: spark-store, amber-pm-store
Homepage: https://github.com/Xynrin/spark-store-tui
Description: Terminal UI for browsing Spark Store and APM Store
 A Bash + fzf terminal UI for browsing Spark Store and APM Store metadata,
 previewing app details and images, and downloading packages with Metalink
 and aria2c.
 .
 Downloads use a temporary directory by default and are cleaned up when the
 program exits unless KEEP_DOWNLOADS=1 is set.
 .
 Debian-like systems default to Spark Store. Non-Debian systems default to
 APM Store only and do not show Spark Store content unless explicitly allowed.
